    <h1>Privacy Policy for SUM1 Score Copier</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> [Current Date]</p>
    
    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p>SUM1 Score Copier does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. All data processing occurs locally within your browser.</p>
    
    <h2>Data Usage</h2>
    <p>The extension temporarily stores numerical scores in your browser's local storage only to facilitate copying data between spreadsheets and web forms. This data is automatically cleared when you close your browser or click "Clear Stored Data".</p>
    
    <h2>Third Party Access</h2>
    <p>No data is shared with third parties. The extension operates entirely within your browser.</p>
    
    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>Since no data is transmitted or stored on external servers, your information remains secure on your device.</p>
    
    <h2>Contact</h2>
